Package: ShennongData
Title: Lazy R Client for Shennong Data Server
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shennong Team [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Shennong Team <shennong@example.org>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Shennong", "Team", email = "shennong@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides tidyverse-style lazy handles for datasets served by
    Shennong Data Server. Dataset handles do not download data until collect,
    fetch, or plotting helpers request bounded pages from the API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    rlang,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
